foods.ingredients: OLD FASHIONED WHITE BREAD: [ENRICHED UNBLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN AND FOLIC ACID)], WATER, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, POTATO FLOUR, VEGETABLE OIL (CANOLA AND/OR SOY), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF EACH OF THE FOLLOWING: YEAST, SALT, EXTRACT OF MALTED BARLEY, DEXTROSE, YEAST NUTRIENT (AMMONIUM SULPHATE), DOUGH CONDITIONERS (MONO-DIGLYCERIDES, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, ASCORBIC ACID, AZODICARBONAMIDE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE), CALCIUM PROPIONATE (MOLD INHIBITOR), CALCIUM SULFATE, ENZYMES, NONFAT DRY MILK, SOY FLOUR., SMOKED HAM: CURED WITH: WATER, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SALT, DEXTROSE, POTASSIUM LACTATE, SUGAR, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM DIACETATE, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE, LIQUID EGGS: WHOLE EGGS, CITRIC ACID, 0.15% WATER ADDED AS CARRIER FOR CITRIC ACID, CITRIC ACID ADDED TO PRESERVE COLOR. TURKEY: WHITE TURKEY, WATER, TURKEY SKIN, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, AND 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: SALT, DEXTROSE, CARRAGEENAN, SODIUM CITRATE, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SUGAR, NATURAL FLAVORING, TAPIOCA STARCH, SODIUM DIACETATE., CHEDDAR CHEESE: PASTEURIZED MILK, SALT, ENZYMES, ANNATTO (COLOR), SWISS CHEESE: PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES. IMITATION VANILLA FLAVOR: WATER, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, VANILLIN, CARAMEL COLOR.
